164
00:09:50,053 --> 00:09:52,353
Ya, kau tidak perlu memberi tahuku.

165
00:09:52,353 --> 00:09:53,853
Bukankah itu aneh?

166
00:09:53,853 --> 00:09:55,053
Apa maksudmu?

167
00:09:55,053 --> 00:09:57,453
Penjaga gawang biasanya memakai nomor 1,

168
00:09:57,453 --> 00:09:59,553
