169
00:09:59,553 --> 00:10:02,653
Ray awalnya adalah gelandang tengah.

170
00:10:02,653 --> 00:10:04,953
Tapi selama Seri Piala Dunia,

171
00:10:04,953 --> 00:10:08,153
